OL,3,CCalls for tougher laws to protect
OL,4,CLGBTQ and disabled islanders
OL,6,FCharlie Murray-Edwards, who is
OL,7,Ftransgender, says insults have been
OL,8,Fhurled at him in St Peter Port, adding
OL,9,Fthere are places on the island he
OL,10,Ffeels like he can't go to.
OL,12,FCharlie explains: "You get the hateful
OL,13,Fcomments and you're walking through
OL,14,Ftown and people who don't know you -
OL,15,Fthey're just assuming - I could've
OL,16,Fjust been a masculine looking woman
OL,17,Fbut they assume I'm trans and they've
OL,18,Fmade a comment and they've shouted a
OL,19,Fslur.
