OL,3,CCalls for tougher laws to protect
OL,4,CLGBTQ and disabled islanders
OL,6,F"It's a small island (and) everyone
OL,7,Fwill run into each other. I can't hide
OL,8,Ffrom the people who hate me - you
OL,9,Fcan't hide in Guernsey - you just have
OL,10,Fto take a different route.
OL,12,F"Friends parents have read the
OL,13,Fmessages that I've been sent and
OL,14,Fthey've had to take action themselves.
OL,16,F"Why is it the community having to
OL,17,Fcome together (...) to protect me
OL,18,Fbecause laws aren't there?"
