OL,3,CCalls for tougher laws to protect
OL,4,CLGBTQ and disabled islanders
OL,6,FLisa Robins, who has multiple
OL,7,Fsclerosis told ITV News that owing to
OL,8,Fher slurred speech she has received
OL,9,Fhurtful comments when she goes out in
OL,10,Fpublic.
OL,12,FShe said: "People just assumed I was
OL,13,Fdrunk and it really annoyed me, a lot
OL,14,Fof it is a lack of education.
OL,16,F"It's just demeaning and very annoying.
OL,18,F"A lot of things (used to) crush me
OL,19,Fbut now I'm very stroppy."
